OL,3,C'I'm still waiting for justice': The
OL,4,Cwomen fighting for pension compensation
OL,6,FAngela Madden, from North Yorkshire,
OL,7,Fis the chair of the WASPI campaign.
OL,8,FShe has said she is "glad" that the
OL,9,Freport is finally out.
OL,11,F"The ombudsman has been working on
OL,12,Fthis investigation for five years now.
OL,13,FThree years ago, in July 2021, he
OL,14,Fidentified that there had been
OL,15,Fmismanaged administration in the
OL,16,FDepartment of Work and Pensions that
OL,17,Fthey didn't communicate with women as
OL,18,Fsoon as they should have, and it's
OL,19,Ftaken a long three years to get to
OL,20,Fthis stage.
