OL,3,C'I'm still waiting for justice': The
OL,4,Cwomen fighting for pension compensation
OL,6,F"I'm glad it's finished, and it's with
OL,7,Fparliament, as it should be, as they
OL,8,Fare the only ones who can make a
OL,9,Fdecision to compensate us."
OL,11,FChristine Smith, the co-ordinator for
OL,12,FTyne & Wear WASPI, said: "When we
OL,13,Fstarted our group in 2015, I didn't
OL,14,Fexpect to be here nine years later,
OL,15,Fbecause I believed in the UK
OL,16,Fdemocratic society, and the UK
OL,17,FGovernment would put something right.
OL,19,F"We will hold parliament into account."
