OL,3,C'I'm still waiting for justice': The
OL,4,Cwomen fighting for pension compensation
OL,6,FWhile for Ellen Russell, she said that
OL,7,Fthe compensation isn't enough and that
OL,8,Fwhat they have been offered is an
OL,9,F"insult."
OL,11,FShe added: "We've had to put every
OL,12,Fsingle penny towards this fight."
OL,14,FHer fellow campaigner, Denise Collins,
OL,15,Fsaid: "I'm not going anywhere till
OL,16,Fthis is sorted out."
